  "description": {
    "en": "FOR YOU Real estate is resenting desirable spacious 1 bedroom type with direct Burj Khalifa View. Peninsula 4 The Plaza is one of the top quality towers in Peninsula community.\n\nPeninsula is located in Business Bay, a central business district in Dubai known for its mix of residential, commercial, and retail establishments. It offers views of the Dubai Canal and has easy accessibility to various parts of the city.\nSelect Group is one of the leading developers in the UAE. Their reputation is built on delivering high-quality projects.\n\nAmenities will include:\n- barbecue areas\n- retail and leisure elements\n- sauna\n- gymnasium\n- children&#39;s pool\n- swimming pools.\n\nPayment plan is available \n\nIn FOR YOU REAL ESTATE \nWe provide a full range of services from consulting and selection of investment-profitable real estate to receiving dividends from your investments.\nAdvantages of working with us:\n - Detailed market analysis — we will select the appropriate object based on your request\n - We will take over the entire transaction process from purchase to sale, marketing placement and rental\n - Many developers have access to exclusive lots and the best options\n - We provide first-class service. We are always for long-term cooperation\n - Our team has the best brokers\n - We have been working in the market with premium clients for a long time\n\nFor You Real Estate L.L.C. is based in The Onyx Tower 2, office 910 with a team of agents who are focused on the sales, rentals and management of properties in Dubai.\nThe portfolio of our services includes:\n* Off-plan sales\n* Secondary market/ resales\n* Leasing\n* Property management\n* Short term leasing."
