  "description": {
    "en": "FOR YOU REAL ESTATE is delighted to present you this elegant 1-bedroom apartment in JVC District 11, Jumeirah Village Circle, Dubai. The apartment has a beautiful view on Five hotel, floor-to-ceiling windows, fully equipped kitchen, and an extra bed. Ideal for couples and families, this luxurious 1-bedroom offers modern style and convenience.\n\n15 minutes away from Mall of the Emirates\n20 minutes away from Dubai Marina\n25 minutes away from Downtown Dubai \n7 minutes away from Circle Mall\n10 minutes away from Dubai Hills Mall\n\nProperty Features: \n- 1 Bedroom with king-size bed\n- 1 Bathroom\n- 1 parking space\n- Smart home\n- Fully furnished\n- Balcony\n- Built-in Wardrobe\n- Black-out curtains\n- Smart TV\n\nBuilding Amenities: \n- Swimming Pool\n- Sun loungers\n- Fully Equipped Gym\n- Kids swimming pool\n- Gazebo \n- 24/7 Security & Concierge service\n\nWithin walking distance:\n- Pharmacy\n- VIVA supermarket\n- Gas station \n- Cafes\n- Community parks\n\nIn FOR YOU REAL ESTATE \nWe provide a full range of services from consulting and selection of investment-profitable real estate to receiving dividends from your investments.\nAdvantages of working with us:\n - Detailed market analysis — we will select the appropriate object based on your request\n - We will take over the entire transaction process from purchase to sale, marketing placement and rental\n - Many developers have access to exclusive lots and the best options\n - We provide first-class service. We are always for long-term cooperation\n - Our team has the best brokers\n - We have been working in the market with premium clients for a long time.\nFor You Real Estate L.L.C. is based in The Onyx Tower 2, office 910 with a team of agents who are focused on the sales, rentals and management of properties in Dubai.\n\n"
  },
