  "description": {
    "en": "FOR YOU Real Estate is proud to present an excellent opportunity to acquire a brand new retail unit in Binghatti Phantom, strategically located next to the main entrance, ensuring high visibility and strong footfall. Ideal for F&B or retail concepts looking to establish a presence in a modern, high-demand development.\n\n- Payment Terms: 4 cheques per year\n- Power load: 21 KW (extendable through DEWA)\n- Gas connection available\n- Fresh air intake and exhaust ducts already installed\n- Wet areas provision with in-unit restroom\n- 4.5-meter ceiling height, ideal for flexible fit-outs\n- F&B permitted\n- 3 dedicated parking spaces on podium level\n\nThis unit offers flexibility for various business concepts and is well suited for investors or end users seeking a high-potential commercial space in a growing area.\nPrime exposure, modern infrastructure, and strong long-term value.\n\nIn FOR YOU REAL ESTATE \nWe provide a full range of services from consulting and selection of investment-profitable real estate to receiving dividends from your investments.\nAdvantages of working with us:\n - Detailed market analysis — we will select the appropriate object based on your request\n - We will take over the entire transaction process from purchase to sale, marketing placement and rental\n - Many developers have access to exclusive lots and the best options\n - We provide first-class service. We are always for long-term cooperation\n - Our team has the best brokers\n - We have been working in the market with premium clients for a long time.\nFor You Real Estate L.L.C. is based in The Onyx Tower 2, office 910 with a team of agents who are focused on the sales, rentals and management of properties in Dubai."
  },
